data.description:
Stunning property featuring breathtaking mountain views and an expansive 44 acres of land. Situated perfectly between the Rifle Gap and Harvey Gap state parks, this residence offers a rare opportunity to experience nature's beauty at its finest. With a well and seven natural springs on the property, water access is abundant, enhancing the appeal of this remarkable estate. This property offers an unrivaled vantage point to soak in the beauty of nature that surrounds you. The main floor features a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house with all the comforts of home. Additionally, the basement features a 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom Accessory Dwelling Unit (ADU) complete with its own private entrance - perfect for guests, extended family, or rental income. Experience the privacy, beauty, and boundless opportunities this property offers. 
Contact us today to schedule your private showing and discover the magic of this remarkable property.
